The White House




May 09, 2009

 



President Meets with Captain Richard Phillips Today




THE WHITE HOUSE  Office of the Press Secretary  ________________________________________________________  For Immediate Release                        May 9, 2009  President Meets with Captain Richard Phillips Today President Barack Obama met with Captain Richard Phillips and his wife Andrea today in the Oval Office. To view a picture of the President’s meeting with Captain Phillips today click HERE.  ###
